        <Historic_Flag>Current</Historic_Flag>
        <Parent_String>igneous rock by composition: physical [300011231], igneous rock by composition [300157789], igneous rock [300011178], rock (inorganic material) [300011692], inorganic material [300010360], materials by composition [300212963], materials (substances) [300010358], Materials (hierarchy name) [300010357], Materials Facet [300264091]</Parent_String>
